videos.description: Ahmed Hill sinks a 3-pointer to give Virginia Tech an 11-8 lead over Notre Dame.
videos.headline: Virginia Tech takes lead on Hill's 3-pointer

videos.description: Virginia Tech's P.J. Horne delivers a one-handed dunk to open up the Hokies' lead over Notre Dame.
videos.headline: Horne slams 1-handed dunk for Virginia Tech

videos.description: TJ Gibbs makes the second of back-to-back 3-pointers for Notre Dame, closing Virginia Tech's lead to 4.
videos.headline: Gibbs nails 3 to put Notre Dame within 4
